snippet.title: Spacejacked - Gameplay Trailer | PS4, PS VITA
snippet.description:
Spacejacked is a super fast-paced ACTION TOWER-DEFENSE game. Play as Dave, a lone technician tasked with protecting his spaceship from being overrun by aliens while it prepares to warp into hyperspace.

http://www.spacejacked.com
